María Rosa Salgado https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mar%C3%ADa_Rosa_Salgado 0 María Rosa Salgado (1929–1995) was a Spanish actress. She appeared in around twenty films including It Happened in Broad Daylight. María_Rosa_Salgado ( 1929 – 1995 ) was a_Spanish_actress .
